Given I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I select 'Female' radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
And I select 'MRI pelvic floor' radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
Then I go to Page 08 of Pelvic MRI
And I click on 'Finding' radio button
And dropdown below 'Finding' is enabled

When I select 'Acute epiploic appendagitis' from the dropdown
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled

And 'Right-lower quadrant' radio button is enabled
And 'Left-lower quadrant' radio button is enabled

And 'Fat equivalent mass' checkbox is enabled
And 'Adjacent soft tissue edema' checkbox is enabled
And 'Thickening of adjacent intestinal wall' checkbox is enabled

And 'Diverticulitis' radio button is enabled
And 'Appendicitis' radio button is enabled
And 'Mesenteric panniculitis' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Fat equivalent mass' checkbox
Then 'Diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Thickened adjacent visceral peritoneum' checkbox is enabled

When I enter '1' in the input field below 'Diameter' checkbox
Then the number is accepted
When I enter '9999' in the input field below 'Diameter' checkbox
Then the number is accepted

When I select 'Mesenteric panniculitis' checkbox
Then 'Subordinate' input field is enabled

